As a user I want:
	1.	to be able to sign up/in/out
		use devise to set up a user model
		have sign up/in/out options on the header
	2.	have a role as a guest, host, or both
		set up column for the user object to include role(s)
	3.	to have a profile with my personal information
		have a profile view

As a airbnb guest I want:
	1.	to see a list of places available to rent
		create an index list will include a representative picture, price, and reviews
	2.	to see a list of experiences to partake in
	3.	to view a list of my upcoming trips
	4.	to be able to view details on each available place to rent including:
		a slide of photos of the place
		link to the renter's profile
		a map of the location
		display reviews
		displayratings
	5.	to be able to view details on experiences
		link to the renter's profile
		a map of the location
		display reviews
		display ratings
	6.	to be able to reach out to the persons renting out their place via message
		have messaging system
	7.	search for places to rent
		by location
		by dates
			by number of guests
	8.	make payments to the host
		set up a payment gateway
	9.	give homes and experiences a rating
		create ratings based on a 5 star scale
	10.	write a review for a home or exprience
		create a review object for a home or experience
	11.	become  a host
		change the status of my account to host
As an airbnb host I want:
	1.	to list my place up for rent or list an experience to host
		create a home or experience listing which includes price, location, photographs
	2.	have a show view of the place I am renting
	3.	to retract/edit a listing
		edit/destroy listing
